{"tid":2075750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢幾日一開熱門睇，起碼有幾個post講冧水壩","createTime":"2020-06-23T05:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T06:08:33.000Z","uid":232167,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"151466b0b1f39cd77621d2d5bd9b87fba377ce2e","tid":2075750,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"個個都越講越興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實三峽大壩崩潰呢個話題都講咗好多年<br />\n<br />\n話你知點解呢度叫<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連燈</span></span>啦，就係因為你哋期望太大，所以先失望越大<br />\n依家淪落到日日都要J大紀元同新唐人呢d媒體咁。佢地反共係一件事，但係有冇吹水成份又係另一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到目前為止，都只係可以確認到中國暴雨成災。但係大家已經諗緊水淹7軍個情況，我建議大家開個三國無雙玩下算。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔可以FF，但係打飛機打得多你都辛苦啦，適可而止。倒不如趁天氣好，落街做運動強身健體，尤其係暑假"},{"pid":"5c2242b52db59145acdfcc4f56ce771689c27cc5","tid":2075750,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77dc84ebde44465f38f7877afdd8507aedea360","tid":2075750,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e46ed605034c4d11b859b27f3531a17854cda42","tid":2075750,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a51bff1a5036fd009a7083f3b8cad1c75923f0","tid":2075750,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e30a1a0ab833606b2ec152302cd6fd1f7c7ba46","tid":2075750,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislik